{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 1961, "height": 2664, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [176, 696, 252, 1381], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "一九五", "block_bbox": [185, 2018, 232, 2116], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "徐坡", "block_bbox": [951, 231, 1196, 291], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "徐坡村，又名杜陵村。位于宜阳县盐镇乡的东南面，是周沟村下属一自然村。因“文革”动乱，杜氏家谱遗失，史无可考，询及长者，曰：相传徐坡杜姓从浙江金华迁来。1972年修焦枝铁路时，托浙江金华杜姓人回乡查问，回信是无证据能证明徐坡杜姓是从浙江迁来的。于是，联系中断。所幸1987年，渑池县坻坞族人续谱。从雪瑶一路寻访，最终访寻到了失散多代的五世三元之次子光衍：光衍亦是徐坡杜氏之祖。另，在徐坡祖坟石碑上明示始祖流芳，坻坞的始祖亦是流芳公，此真乃是一脉相承，绝非巧合。自此，徐坡杜姓才得以认祖归宗。\n", "block_bbox": [338, 361, 1798, 791], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "至2008年10月，徐坡村各姓有213户人家，525口人，土地面积380多亩。杜氏人口包括会卦、周过共503人，其中男254人、女249人。\n", "block_bbox": [342, 804, 1795, 919], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "徐坡村杜氏始祖为渑池坻坞杜氏五世三元之次子光衍。", "block_bbox": [426, 935, 1384, 982], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "其世系为流芳公——忠——果——真银——三元(三派)——光衍。", "block_bbox": [426, 998, 1589, 1048], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "光衍于清初期迁至徐坡，坟茔在徐坡之鞍桥山安家沟。", "block_bbox": [430, 1065, 1366, 1112], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 8}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9123964905738831, "coordinate": [338.6832275390625, 361.217041015625, 1798.3358154296875, 791.763